<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your Email - Emboost</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; color: #333333;">
    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center" width="100%" style="max-width: 600px; margin: auto; background-color: #ffffff;">
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 40px 30px;">
                <h2 style="margin: 0 0 20px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; color: #333333;">Verify Your Email Address</h2>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 20px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;">Thank you for signing up with Emboost! To complete your registration, please use the verification code below:</p>
                <div style="background-color: #f0f0f0; border-radius: 4px; padding: 20px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <span style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 5px; color: #4f46e5;"><%= user.verificationCode %></span>
                </div>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 20px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;">If you didn't request this verification, please ignore this email.</p>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 20px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;">If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
                <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;">Best regards,<br>The Emboost Team</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 30px; background-color: #f4f4f4; text-align: center;">
                <p style="margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 14px; color: #666666;">Â© 2025 Emboost. All rights reserved.</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>